{"tid":1838620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我同你講， 肺炎唔會令呢場運動完","createTime":"2020-01-24T05:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T15:25:17.000Z","uid":89105,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0ce95fc4de2689a6d8062035b37ae593725af0","tid":1838620,"uid":89105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"中共好開心啦， 以為香港人依家淨係掛住抗疫唔理場運動？<br />\n唔好白痴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人係唔會忘記六大訴求架！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n六大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人既憤怒一直存在<br />\n武漢肺炎 ，只會令我地更加憎恨中國<br />\n令更多香港人企出黎呀！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38090ae614c32623028cff870063b660af28ab3e","tid":1838620,"uid":89105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">落黎播疫以為可以間接令場運動完？<br />\n咪傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"90e8057c77a9829471d8bcac9fa7eea2e8e9844c","tid":1838620,"uid":293677,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:53:22.000Z","msg":"肺炎係會令中共玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64acfe3e46b39e6d799ff9c09a6c4b9d54eaee15","tid":1838620,"uid":89105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90e8057